These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
Beverage: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
Birthday: april, august, june, december
1. Beverage:hot-chocolate is between Beverage:cola and Birthday:august##2
2. Beverage:hot-chocolate is on the left or right of Birthday:april##3
3. Beverage:hot-chocolate is somewhere between Beverage:tea and Beverage:cola##7
4. Birthday:august is in an even position##4
5. Beverage:tea is on the right of Birthday:june##1
6. Birthday:august is somewhere to the left of Birthday:april##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Birthday      | june  | august | december        | april |

