.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
Flower: balloon-flower, zinnia, sunflower, orchid
Sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. Sport:volleyball is somewhere between Sport:skateboarding and Flower:sunflower##7
2. Flower:orchid is somewhere to the left of Flower:balloon-flower##5
3. Flower:orchid is somewhere to the right of Sport:volleyball##5
4. Flower:zinnia is on the left of Flower:orchid##1
5. Sport:volleyball is between Sport:skateboarding and Sport:rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Flower     | sunflower | zinnia       | orchid         | balloon-flower     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

