.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
Music-Genre: reggae, d&b, blues, hip-hop
Sport: climbing, golf, skateboarding, volleyball
1. Sport:volleyball is on the far left or far right##3
2. Music-Genre:reggae is somewhere between Sport:golf and Music-Genre:hip-hop##7
3. Music-Genre:blues == Sport:volleyball##1
4. Sport:skateboarding is on the left of Sport:volleyball##1
5. Music-Genre:d&b is on the left of Sport:climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | reggae | hip-hop       | blues |
| Sport   | golf      | climbing   | skateboarding | volleyball  |

