3. Music-Genre:salsa != Movie-Genre:thriller##6
4. Movie-Genre:thriller is somewhere to the right of Music-Genre:funk##5
5. Movie-Genre:family == Music-Genre:jazz##1
6. Movie-Genre:western is somewhere to the right of Music-Genre:jazz##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | western | satire | thriller |
| Music-Genre           | jazz    | salsa   | funk  | classical      |

